WEBVTT

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:11.200
Kid, give your dad a call.

00:01:11.799 --> 00:01:12.959
Uncle needs to talk to him.

00:01:13.760 --> 00:01:15.439
You gave someone my number!

00:01:17.400 --> 00:01:18.799
Stealing my money? Speak!

00:01:20.920 --> 00:01:22.400
Stop hitting Sister!

00:01:22.599 --> 00:01:24.239
Don't hit Sister!

00:01:25.400 --> 00:01:26.840
I took the money.

00:01:26.840 --> 00:01:28.519
Sister didn't take it.

00:01:28.840 --> 00:01:30.280
So you were in on it too.

00:01:30.799 --> 00:01:32.519
Come here! I'm gonna beat you to death!

00:01:32.519 --> 00:01:33.159
Don't hit my little sister!

00:01:33.159 --> 00:01:34.400
Stealing at such a young age.

00:01:35.400 --> 00:01:37.040
You're no good, just like your mom.

00:01:40.200 --> 00:01:41.159
I'll beat you to death!

00:01:44.599 --> 00:01:45.640
I'll teach you to steal!

00:01:50.200 --> 00:01:51.359
Sister.

00:01:51.359 --> 00:01:53.359
Sister, where are you going?

00:01:53.640 --> 00:01:55.280
Don't leave me behind.

00:01:57.200 --> 00:01:59.280
Don't leave me behind.

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:01.799
Don't leave me behind.

00:02:01.920 --> 00:02:02.560
Xiao Ran.

00:02:04.200 --> 00:02:05.439
I don't want to leave either.

00:02:06.359 --> 00:02:07.280
I swear.

00:02:07.879 --> 00:02:08.520
In the future,

00:02:09.159 --> 00:02:09.840
I will definitely take you

00:02:09.840 --> 00:02:11.840
to live in the place closest to the sky.

00:02:12.919 --> 00:02:14.400
A house like a castle.

00:02:15.479 --> 00:02:18.240
We'll have endless money then.

00:02:19.360 --> 00:02:20.840
We'll never go hungry again.

00:02:22.680 --> 00:02:23.800
After I persuaded her,

00:02:24.599 --> 00:02:25.680
Sister stayed.

00:02:27.319 --> 00:02:28.199
Not long after,

00:02:28.759 --> 00:02:29.879
Dad went missing.

00:02:30.960 --> 00:02:33.520
Sister said Dad, to hide from loan sharks,

00:02:33.520 --> 00:02:34.439
abandoned us.

00:02:35.560 --> 00:02:36.280
Later on,

00:02:37.599 --> 00:02:39.000
someone in the mountains on the outskirts

00:02:40.000 --> 00:02:40.599
Xiao Ran,

00:02:40.599 --> 00:02:41.680
found Dad's body.

00:02:42.479 --> 00:02:44.080
Regarding your father's death,

00:02:44.319 --> 00:02:45.639
Auntie is deeply sorry.

00:02:46.039 --> 00:02:48.039
Since we couldn't contact your mother,

00:02:48.039 --> 00:02:49.840
the community contacted us.

00:02:50.199 --> 00:02:51.080
Today, Auntie

00:02:51.080 --> 00:02:53.639
is here to take you to your new home, Hongshan Welfare Society.

00:02:54.240 --> 00:02:56.039
You will live there for a while.

00:02:56.639 --> 00:02:57.639
For a while?

00:02:58.360 --> 00:02:59.319
And after that?

00:02:59.599 --> 00:03:01.159
The Welfare Society will find you

00:03:01.159 --> 00:03:02.280
new parents.

00:03:02.719 --> 00:03:04.680
So you can have a home of your own again.

00:03:05.479 --> 00:03:06.840
Then can we go to school?

00:03:07.960 --> 00:03:08.840
Of course.

00:03:39.719 --> 00:03:40.360
Xiao Ran

00:03:42.120 --> 00:03:43.360
I heard from Auntie Zhang

00:03:43.360 --> 00:03:45.639
that a well-off family has taken a liking to you

00:03:45.879 --> 00:03:47.479
They might adopt you

00:03:48.560 --> 00:03:49.439
Listen to me

00:03:50.039 --> 00:03:51.319
You must be very good

00:03:51.639 --> 00:03:52.639
Very obedient

00:03:52.879 --> 00:03:54.039
You must go with them

00:03:54.800 --> 00:03:56.280
But what about you, sister?

00:03:58.400 --> 00:03:59.240
Don't worry

00:03:59.439 --> 00:04:01.680
No matter where you go, I will find you

00:04:01.680 --> 00:04:03.400
I will protect you for the rest of my life

00:04:10.439 --> 00:04:11.439
We won't be in touch anymore

00:04:15.319 --> 00:04:16.120
I have a question

00:04:17.319 --> 00:04:19.040
Is your new home far from the welfare institute?

00:04:19.839 --> 00:04:22.759
My home is in the same city as the Welfare Society

00:04:23.879 --> 00:04:24.639
Later on

00:04:25.800 --> 00:04:27.319
My sister was also adopted soon after

00:04:27.680 --> 00:04:28.560
And moved to Tai Cheng

00:04:30.439 --> 00:04:31.439
In the first few years

00:04:32.199 --> 00:04:34.279
We still wrote to each other regularly

00:04:35.759 --> 00:04:37.680
But after I transferred to the girls' boarding school

00:04:38.600 --> 00:04:39.879
My studies were heavy

00:04:40.439 --> 00:04:41.519
And the school had many rules

00:04:42.560 --> 00:04:43.480
So we contacted each other less

00:04:43.720 --> 00:04:45.120
Why didn't you go look for her?

00:04:46.360 --> 00:04:47.839
She seemed to always avoid me

00:04:48.279 --> 00:04:49.439
And refused to meet me

00:04:50.800 --> 00:04:51.519
Eventually

00:04:53.120 --> 00:04:54.240
We lost contact completely

00:04:55.000 --> 00:04:57.120
When Di Fu told me this back then

00:04:57.240 --> 00:04:58.240
I didn't quite believe it

00:04:58.319 --> 00:04:59.480
Now that I've heard you finish

00:05:00.040 --> 00:05:00.800
I believe it

00:05:01.720 --> 00:05:04.800
I didn't expect your childhoods to be so tragic

00:05:09.680 --> 00:05:10.839
Poor children

00:05:11.600 --> 00:05:12.639
Drink this

00:05:13.279 --> 00:05:15.079
You'll be fine after drinking it

00:05:22.399 --> 00:05:23.040
It seems

00:05:24.959 --> 00:05:27.240
Your stories are finished

00:05:28.120 --> 00:05:28.800
Then let me say a few words

00:05:30.519 --> 00:05:31.639
I've been a police officer for so many years

00:05:32.800 --> 00:05:34.279
Heard too many stories

00:05:34.639 --> 00:05:35.800
Seen too many truths

00:05:37.040 --> 00:05:39.439
Actually, these stories themselves aren't important

00:05:41.279 --> 00:05:43.319
What's important is what each story

00:05:44.959 --> 00:05:46.319
can bring to the storyteller

00:05:49.600 --> 00:05:51.000
What does that mean?

00:05:52.240 --> 00:05:53.279
You are trapped here

00:05:53.439 --> 00:05:55.519
Isn't it because of Zhao Qishan and his wife's inheritance?

00:05:56.160 --> 00:05:57.600
Since the goal is the same

00:05:59.040 --> 00:06:02.480
the story itself holds no importance

00:06:03.120 --> 00:06:03.839
Does it?

00:06:05.040 --> 00:06:06.639
Inspector Qi implies something

00:06:07.959 --> 00:06:09.600
Could it be that regarding Zhao Qishan and his wife

00:06:09.920 --> 00:06:11.639
Inspector Qi also has a story about them?

00:06:12.199 --> 00:06:14.600
I only have investigation results

00:06:15.399 --> 00:06:16.279
What results?

00:06:19.720 --> 00:06:20.800
Miss Li is right

00:06:21.839 --> 00:06:24.240
She and her sister were indeed adopted separately

00:06:25.000 --> 00:06:26.040
It's just that Miss Li

00:06:27.439 --> 00:06:28.800
her adoptive parents were very good

00:06:28.800 --> 00:06:30.040
and gave her a happy home

00:06:31.279 --> 00:06:32.040
While her sister

00:06:33.560 --> 00:06:34.600
was not so lucky

00:06:35.560 --> 00:06:36.600
After the incident

00:06:37.800 --> 00:06:39.480
I collected some information on the deceased

00:06:41.199 --> 00:06:42.600
After Di Fu was adopted

00:06:43.160 --> 00:06:44.399
her adoptive parents

00:06:45.040 --> 00:06:46.240
both died accidentally

00:06:48.160 --> 00:06:51.040
She didn't tell me that

00:06:54.399 --> 00:06:56.399
I understand what Inspector Qi means

00:06:57.000 --> 00:06:59.040
Is it that Di Fu's adoptive parents

00:06:59.399 --> 00:07:01.040
were killed by her own hand?

00:07:01.759 --> 00:07:03.439
Zhao Qihai, what nonsense are you talking?

00:07:05.000 --> 00:07:06.240
I'm just stating facts

00:07:06.360 --> 00:07:08.199
Without evidence, you really can't speak recklessly

00:07:12.600 --> 00:07:14.480
Inspector Qi, what's wrong?

00:07:34.839 --> 00:07:36.279
It's poisoned! It's poisoned!

00:07:58.240 --> 00:07:59.120
You're awake.

00:07:59.920 --> 00:08:02.000
Auntie Ma, you drugged us.

00:08:06.240 --> 00:08:07.680
What are you doing, you crazy bitch?

00:08:08.160 --> 00:08:09.000
Don't be afraid.

00:08:10.439 --> 00:08:12.680
I just wanted you all to quiet down.

00:08:13.279 --> 00:08:14.560
This is getting interesting.

00:08:14.959 --> 00:08:15.920
What's so interesting?

00:08:16.240 --> 00:08:18.639
Didn't I say we should kick her out?

00:08:18.839 --> 00:08:19.839
No one listened.

00:08:21.000 --> 00:08:21.600
Let me tell you.

00:08:21.600 --> 00:08:22.519
The police are here.

00:08:22.920 --> 00:08:23.920
What can you do to us?

00:08:25.480 --> 00:08:26.639
Di Fu is just a bitch.

00:08:27.360 --> 00:08:28.920
Keeping a lunatic like you around.

00:08:29.360 --> 00:08:31.040
You should be just like your daughter.

00:08:31.360 --> 00:08:33.480
Hurry up and disappear from this world.

00:08:37.440 --> 00:08:38.600
Where is my daughter?

00:08:41.399 --> 00:08:42.200
I don't know.

00:08:42.840 --> 00:08:45.080
If you don't know, keep your mouth shut.

00:08:47.159 --> 00:08:47.799
Also...

00:08:48.799 --> 00:08:50.440
Don't call me a crazy bitch.

00:08:50.440 --> 00:08:51.039
I know.

00:08:56.639 --> 00:08:57.440
Don't be scared.

00:08:58.519 --> 00:09:00.080
I just wanted him to behave.

00:09:08.600 --> 00:09:10.039
It's Lawyer Luo.

00:09:23.279 --> 00:09:26.039
Alright, no one will disturb us now.

00:09:26.320 --> 00:09:28.879
Auntie Ma, just name your demands.

00:09:29.879 --> 00:09:31.200
I want to know the truth.

00:09:31.200 --> 00:09:32.679
What truth do you want exactly?

00:09:33.159 --> 00:09:35.000
I want to know the truth about my daughter.

00:09:36.080 --> 00:09:37.200
Here, besides you...

00:09:37.399 --> 00:09:38.639
Besides the dead Di Fu...

00:09:39.720 --> 00:09:41.720
Is there anyone else connected to Nana?

00:09:47.240 --> 00:09:48.559
Look closely.

00:09:48.559 --> 00:09:49.679
Do you recognize my daughter?

00:09:50.200 --> 00:09:51.519
Do you recognize her or not?

00:09:51.519 --> 00:09:53.600
Auntie, I... I know the person in the photo.

00:09:53.600 --> 00:09:56.279
But she... she... she's called Lin Niannian.

00:09:56.279 --> 00:09:57.440
Auntie, Lin Niannian.

00:09:57.720 --> 00:09:58.799
Lin Niannian is...

00:09:58.799 --> 00:10:00.799
You finally said it.

00:10:01.480 --> 00:10:02.840
What is your relationship with Niannian?

00:10:03.159 --> 00:10:04.240
Friends, friends.

00:10:04.240 --> 00:10:05.840
Good friends, Auntie. Good friends.

00:10:06.039 --> 00:10:07.120
Since you were friends...

00:10:07.919 --> 00:10:10.399
Why wasn't she mentioned in your story?

00:10:10.399 --> 00:10:12.200
We were talking about Mr. Zhao... Mr. Zhao.

00:10:12.519 --> 00:10:13.639
About Mr. Zhao and Di Fu.

00:10:13.840 --> 00:10:15.240
Lin Niannian didn't appear in that story.

00:10:15.240 --> 00:10:16.840
Th-th-that's why I didn't say anything.

00:10:17.039 --> 00:10:17.639
That's why I didn't say anything.

00:10:19.639 --> 00:10:21.919
You met Di Fu at a food stall?

00:10:21.919 --> 00:10:22.279
Yes.

00:10:22.799 --> 00:10:23.120
Yes.

00:10:23.120 --> 00:10:25.080
Di Fu has always been a content creator.

00:10:25.360 --> 00:10:27.200
She never worked at any food stall.

00:10:27.279 --> 00:10:27.759
Don't!